《'''塗鴉跳躍'''》（{{lang-en|''Doodle Jump''}}）是由Lima Sky開發的一款電子遊戲，支持[[Windows_Phone|Windows Phone]]、[[iOS|iOS]]、[[黑莓手機|BlackBerry]]、[[Android|Android]]、Java Mobile（[[Java_ME|J2ME]]）、諾基亞[[Symbian|Symbian]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]等平台，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://123kinect.com/doodle-jump-for-kinect/|title=Doodle Jump is coming to Kinect|date=2011-03-15|access-date=2017-07-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110519233425/http://123kinect.com/doodle-jump-for-kinect/|archive-date=2011-05-19|dead-url=yes}}</ref>其作者為[[克羅埃西亞人|克羅埃西亞人]]Igor和Marko Pusenjak。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://allthingsd.com/20100405/meet-the-app-store-millionaires-the-brothers-behind-doodle-jump/|title=Meet the App Store Millionaires: The Brothers Behind Doodle Jump|last=Kafla|first=Peter|website=allthingsd.com|publisher=AllThingsD|date=2010-04-05|accessdate=2015-03-29|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402112104/http://allthingsd.com/20100405/meet-the-app-store-millionaires-the-brothers-behind-doodle-jump/|dead-url=no}}</ref>遊戲於2009年4月6日在iOS全球發行，之後於2010年3月2日在Android和Blackberry平台發佈。遊戲在Symbian平台發佈的時間為2010年5月1日，在Windows Phone 7上則於2011年6月1日發佈<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.windowscentral.com/doodle-jump-has-landed-marketplace |title=Doodle Jump has landed on the Marketplace |last=Acevedo |first=Paul |date=2011-06-01 |work=Windows Central |publisher=Mobile Nations |accessdate=2011-06-04 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130174720/https://www.windowscentral.com/doodle-jump-has-landed-marketplace |dead-url=no }}</ref>（2013年8月21日在Windows Phone 8上重新發佈）。<ref>{{cite_web|url=http://www.windowscentral.com/doodle-jump-windows-phone-8-loses-xboxlive|title=Doodle Jump hops back onto Windows Phone 8, but drops Xbox Live support|last=Edmonds|first=Rich|date=2013-08-21|accessdate=2013-08-22|work=Windows Central|publisher=Mobile Nations|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127174439/https://www.windowscentral.com/doodle-jump-windows-phone-8-loses-xboxlive|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite_web|url=https://mspoweruser.com/doodle-jump-now-available-for-windows-phone-8-devices/comment-page-1/|title=Doodle Jump Now Available For Windows Phone 8 Devices|author=Pradeep|publisher=MSPoweruser|date=2013-08-21|accessdate=2017-01-09|archive-date=2019-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813153925/https://mspoweruser.com/doodle-jump-now-available-for-windows-phone-8-devices/comment-page-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2011年9月1日，遊戲在iPad上發佈。遊戲的玩法靈感最初源於{{tsl|en|Sunflat Games||Sunflat Games}}的《PapiJump》，其角色靈感則源於伊丽丝·格繪製的插圖。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://elisegravel.com/en/doodlegarage|title=Elise Gravel's Illustrations|accessdate=2014-02-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140219102421/http://elisegravel.com/en/doodlegarage|archivedate=2014-02-19}}</ref>

在《塗鴉跳躍》中，玩家操控一隻名為“The Doodler”的四腳動物在一個永無休止的平台上一直跳高。如果The Doodler墮下，則遊戲結束。跳得越高，遊戲的分數便越高。The Doodler可由控制遊戲設備的傾斜度而移動的。在黑莓版本，則是由方向鍵控制。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://toucharcade.com/2009/03/20/doodle-jump-takes-papijump-to-the-next-level |title=Doodle Jump Takes PapiJump to the Next Level |last=Kim |first=Arnold |date=2009-03-20 |publisher=TouchArcade |accessdate=2010-03-09 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205150200/https://toucharcade.com/2009/03/20/doodle-jump-takes-papijump-to-the-next-level/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamezebo.com/2009/12/31/doodle-jump-review/ |title=Doodle Jump Review |last=Cowdell |first=Lisa |date=2009-12-31 |publisher=[[Gamezebo|Gamezebo]] |accessdate=2010-03-09 |archive-date=2018-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613161306/https://www.gamezebo.com/2009/12/31/doodle-jump-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《塗鴉跳躍》在App Store上曾連續4個月日銷量達到25,000份。截至2011年12月，遊戲在[[iTunes|iTunes]]和[[Google_Play|Google Play]]上銷量已達到1000萬，在全部平台上銷量總和達到1500萬。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thesixthaxis.com/2011/03/16/doodle-jump-sales-hit-10-million-heads-to-xbox-360/|title=Doodle Jump Sales Hit 10 Million, Heads To Xbox 360|work=thesixthaxis.com|access-date=2017-07-19|archive-date=2019-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190813201108/http://www.thesixthaxis.com/2011/03/16/doodle-jump-sales-hit-10-million-heads-to-xbox-360/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/16/doodle-jump-hits-10-million-sales-propelled-onto-xbla/|title=Doodle Jump hits 10 million sales, propelled onto XBLA|work=VG247.com|last=Hillier|first=Brenna|date=2011-03-16|accessdate=2011-03-17|archive-date=2020-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200920152436/https://www.vg247.com/2011/03/16/doodle-jump-hits-10-million-sales-propelled-onto-xbla/|dead-url=no}}</ref>遊戲發行後收穫了外界的好評，[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]根據6個評論給出遊戲85.00%的好評率。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerankings.com/iphone/969788-doodle-jump/index.html|title=Doodle Jump|work=gamerankings.com|access-date=2017-07-19|archive-date=2019-12-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191209014512/https://www.gamerankings.com/iphone/969788-doodle-jump/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

